  "prompt": "Where can I buy funky birthday gifts within Rs. 2000?",
  "response": "Okay, finding funky gifts under Rs. 2000 is definitely doable! Here's a breakdown of where to look, categorized for easier browsing, along with specific ideas within that price range:\n\n**I. Online Marketplaces (Great for Variety & Convenience):**\n\n*   **Amazon.in:**\n    *   **Search Keywords:** \"unique birthday gifts,\" \"quirky gifts,\" \"funny gifts,\" \"novelty gifts,\" \"gifts for [recipient's interest],\" \"birthday gifts under 2000\"\n    *   **Gift Ideas:**\n        *   **Funky Desk Organizers:**  Animal-shaped pen holders, mini basketball hoop wastebasket, quirky bookends.\n        *   **Novelty Lights:**  String lights with fun shapes (stars, animals, emojis), a small lava lamp, a projector night light.\n        *   **Unique Mugs:**  Heat-changing mugs, mugs with funny sayings, mugs shaped like animals or objects.\n        *   **Board games and card games:** Many games are under Rs.2000\n\n*   **Flipkart.com:**\n    *   **Similar approach to Amazon:** Use similar keywords to search.\n    *   **Gift Ideas:**\n        *   **Tech Gadgets & Accessories:** Cool phone stands, funky earphones, personalized phone cases.\n        *   **Personalized Items:**  Customized keychains, photo frames with funny captions, printed cushions.\n        *   **Hampers and Combos:** They often have pre-made gift boxes with a mix of small, fun items (chocolates, snacks, trinkets).\n\n*   **Etsy.com:**\n    *   **Focus:** Handmade, Vintage, and Unique items.  (Remember to factor in potential shipping costs and delivery times!)\n    *   **Search Keywords:** \"quirky gifts,\" \"personalized gifts,\" \"handmade [type of gift],\" \"funny [type of gift]\"\n    *   **Gift Ideas:**\n        *   **Handmade Jewelry:**  Funky earrings, necklaces with unusual pendants (e.g., tiny food items, miniature tools).\n        *   **Custom Stickers or Patches:**  For a personal touch on laptops, bags, or clothing.\n        *   **Unique Home Decor:**  Small, quirky planters, hand-painted coasters, funny wall art prints.\n\n*   **Myntra.com:**\n    *   **Focus:** Apparel, Accessories, Lifestyle Products\n    *   **Gift Ideas:**\n        *   **Funky Socks:** Novelty socks with crazy patterns or characters.\n        *   **Statement T-shirts:** T-shirts with funny quotes, pop culture references, or unique designs.\n        *   **Cool Sunglasses:**  Trendy or retro-style sunglasses.\n        *   **Funky Bags & Wallets:**  Backpacks with interesting prints or designs, wallets with bold colors or patterns.\n\n*   **The Souled Store:**\n    *   **Focus:** Officially licensed merchandise (movies, TV shows, comics, etc.) and quirky apparel.\n    *   **Gift Ideas:**  T-shirts, mugs, posters, phone cases, backpacks featuring popular characters or franchises.\n\n**II. Specialty Gift Shops (For More Curated Selection):**\n\n*   **ThinkGeek (International, but ships to India):**\n    *   **Focus:**  Science, technology, and pop culture themed gifts.\n    *   **Things to Consider:** Shipping costs and import duties can add up, so be mindful of your budget.\n\n*   **Local Gift Shops/Boutiques:**\n    *   **Advantage:**  You can see and touch the items before buying, and support local businesses.\n    *   **How to Find:**  Search online for \"gift shops near me,\" \"unique gifts [your city],\" \"quirky gifts [your city].\"\n    *   **Possible Gifts:**  Handcrafted items, locally made art, imported novelty items.\n\n**III. Experiential Gifts (Memorable & Fun - Can fit within budget):**\n\n*   **Book a Fun Activity:**\n    *   **Options:** Go-karting, bowling, escape room, pottery class, cooking class, wine tasting (if applicable).\n    *   **Where to Find:** Bookmyshow, Nearbuy, LBB (Little Black Book - a good resource for city-specific experiences).\n\n*   **Tickets to a Show/Event:**\n    *   **Options:** Comedy show, concert by a local band, theater performance, film festival.\n\n**IV. DIY (If You're Crafty):**\n\n*   **Personalized Photo Album/Scrapbook:**  Fill it with memories and funny captions.\n*   **Handmade Gift Basket:**  Curate a collection of small, quirky items.\n*   **Decorated Mason Jars:**  Fill them with candies, cookies, or other treats.\n\n**Tips for Finding the Perfect Funky Gift within Budget:**\n\n1.  **Consider the Recipient's Personality:**  What are their hobbies, interests, and sense of humor? Tailor the gift to their individual style.\n2.  **Read Reviews:** Before buying anything online, check the reviews to make sure the quality is good.\n3.  **Compare Prices:** Don't just buy the first thing you see. Shop around to find the best deal.\n4.  **Check for Sales and Discounts:** Many online retailers offer discounts, especially during holidays and special events.\n5.  **Factor in Shipping Costs:**  If buying online, be sure to include shipping costs in your budget.\n6.  **Presentation Matters:**  Even a simple gift can feel special if it's wrapped nicely or presented in a creative way. Use funky wrapping paper, ribbons, or tags to add a personal touch.\n7.  **Don't Be Afraid to Get Creative:** Think outside the box and come up with a gift that's truly unique and memorable.\n\n**Example Gift Ideas within Budget (Based on Categories):**\n\n*   **For the Tea/Coffee Lover:** A novelty tea infuser (shaped like a shark, rubber duck, etc.) + a bag of unique tea/coffee.\n*   **For the Desk Jockey:** A mini desktop punching bag or a stress ball shaped like a funny emoji.\n*   **For the Movie Buff:** A set of movie-themed socks + a pack of their favorite popcorn.\n*   **For the Gamer:** A set of novelty dice or a funny gaming-themed t-shirt.\n*   **For the Bookworm:** A quirky bookmark or a book-shaped lamp.\n\nBy following these tips and exploring the options above, you should be able to find a fantastic and funky birthday gift within your budget!  Good luck!\n",
